Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.29,0:00:02.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.21,0:00:06.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,接纳那个名叫西露卡的魔法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.33,0:00:08.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对同盟来说才算上策吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.46,0:00:13.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果认可宣称隶属联合并扩大领地的君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.51,0:00:17.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,便无法抑制效仿的君主了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.47,0:00:23.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,假如听从你的意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.06,0:00:26.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就必须讨伐提欧•科尔内罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.56,0:00:31.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你的养女恐怕会跟君主患难与共吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.53,0:00:32.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.03,0:00:35.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我已有觉悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.58,0:00:41.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,宣告我方的决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.08,0:00:44.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧•科尔内罗归顺瓦尔林德王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.96,0:00:47.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,以及加入大工房同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.00,0:00:49.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我方无法认可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.75,0:00:52.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,推荐你方奉还领土和爵位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.05,0:00:56.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,速速离开塞维斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.72,0:01:00.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,否则  为了夺回塞维斯的领地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.26,0:01:02.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我方会让瓦尔林德骑士团全军出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.14,0:01:05.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,以讨伐提欧・科尔内罗子爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.56,0:01:10.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你做得太过火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.53,0:01:16.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾我方无法听从您的建议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.45,0:01:22.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,下次就在战场上相见吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,真心难以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.42,0:02:58.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那人总是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.13,0:03:01.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,契约魔法师应该抛弃私情的道理我懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.76,0:03:03.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是太过火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.68,0:03:05.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说父亲坏话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.05,0:03:09.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,同盟不行的话去求联合就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.43,0:03:11.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔・康斯坦斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.43,0:03:14.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那个好色伯爵愿意跟我们结盟吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.65,0:03:23.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,玛格丽特前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.74,0:03:28.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,伯爵说现在不想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.91,0:03:29.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.74,0:03:32.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为加人同盟失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.50,0:03:35.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还真有脸跑到这里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.62,0:03:40.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟首选方案失败后就只能尝试备选方案了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.59,0:03:44.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,如果提欧大人活下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.17,0:03:46.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,克莱榭家将威严扫地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.43,0:03:49.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能延缓同盟团结的进程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.72,0:03:54.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是拯救你的君主对伯爵有好处咯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.48,0:03:55.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.69,0:03:59.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,若不这样做 伯爵家会在不久的将来灭亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.90,0:04:01.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,放肆 小丫头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.32,0:04:05.32,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔大人可是军事家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.45,0:04:09.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不会轻易败给同盟的君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.45,0:04:10.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你说那个好色伯爵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.16,0:04:17.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道魔法大学是怎么称呼维拉尔伯爵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.62,0:04:21.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过阿尔图克盛行魔女信仰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.34,0:04:23.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,伯爵为了获得领民理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.63,0:04:26.67,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一直只跟女性魔法师签订契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.92,0:04:31.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…我听说过了 25岁就会解除契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.10,0:04:35.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,终生契约的话就不能结婚生子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.31,0:04:38.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,伯爵认为这样很对不起对方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.28,0:04:52.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔林德边境伯爵会随塞维斯王一起攻过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.28,0:04:55.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就在这座城迎战他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.75,0:04:59.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,对方总兵力至少两万吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.87,0:05:02.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们顶多三干吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.79,0:05:06.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还要面对瓦尔林德的重装骑士啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.59,0:05:09.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,正面冲突的话根本没法打啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.43,0:05:12.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,是的因此基本上是场守城战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.18,0:05:14.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拉席克阁下负责西门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.43,0:05:17.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,内曼阁下负责东门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.56,0:05:21.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾雪拉和佣兵队请保护好南面的正门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.90,0:05:26.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要让对方明白我们很难应付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.32,0:05:27.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是投降了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.32,0:05:30.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也能让对方答应一定的条件吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起创造奇迹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.59,0:05:53.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没有全军出击？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.22,0:05:57.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在提防阿尔图克伯爵的援军吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.64,0:06:00.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没可能不知道谈判破裂一事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了  大伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.37,0:06:14.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,开始攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.66,0:06:15.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,开始攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.47,0:06:36.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,撑不了多久啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.51,0:06:39.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙先撤退等待西露卡的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.69,0:06:49.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来带你们上路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.65,0:07:32.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.74,0:07:36.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.53,0:07:39.53,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.12,0:07:41.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.91,0:07:45.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西露卡就用不着跟来了  听话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.17,0:07:50.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾雪拉  别死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.42,0:07:52.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,快睁开眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.55,0:07:55.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我来治好那人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.64,0:08:06.10,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有必须履行的责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.35,0:08:09.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,请停留在大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.16,0:08:21.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾雪拉就交给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.88,0:08:33.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.34,0:08:37.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.19,0:08:52.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退  撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.11,0:08:56.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.49,0:09:00.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,总算逼退敌人了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.45,0:09:02.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.28,0:09:03.16,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.04,0:09:08.75,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,报告  西门的内曼阁下战死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.08,0:09:10.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,内曼阁下他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.29,0:09:11.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会・・・
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.79,0:09:13.00,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,西门正在苦战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.21,0:09:14.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,门已被突破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拉席克阁下正在撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.76,0:09:18.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,连拉席克都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.05,0:09:21.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,埃文克拉克队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.27,0:09:28.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退  撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.60,0:09:30.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,逃到死为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.19,0:09:33.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气杀上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.53,0:09:41.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拉席克大人  是时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,停止撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.37,0:09:46.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里迎击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.71,0:09:55.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,一对一的话 拉席克大人可不会输哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.46,0:09:58.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,后退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.76,0:10:01.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在宽阔地带凭数量压制他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.91,0:10:32.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想断掉退路吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.30,0:10:39.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,拿剑来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.97,0:10:43.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,塞维斯王受死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.47,0:10:45.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看人小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.03,0:11:46.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然杀了塞维斯王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.87,0:11:50.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把夺来的圣印献给提欧大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.62,0:11:53.29,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不希望你能收下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.58,0:11:54.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.62,0:11:57.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在杀死塞维斯王之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.79,0:11:59.88,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,从某种意义来说我们获得了胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.00,0:12:06.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们接下来该考虑的是停战协定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.55,0:12:10.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那么需要怎样的条件才能让瓦尔林德撤军呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.39,0:12:15.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是提欧大人保留最低限度的爵位并离开此地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.39,0:12:21.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来塞维斯的所有君主就会归顺瓦尔林德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.11,0:12:24.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望拉席克阁下可以先独立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后担任塞维斯的盟主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.86,0:12:31.28,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么 抛弃一切 提欧大人究竟还剩什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.08,0:12:33.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,能留下名声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.54,0:12:37.37,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,横空岀世的年轻流浪君主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.54,0:12:41.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,英勇抵抗了瓦尔林德的重装骑士团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.38,0:12:43.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要留下了这样的名声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.42,0:12:45.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就能够随时东山再起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,留下的不止这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.68,0:12:48.80,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还有什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.13,0:12:50.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还能留下你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.64,0:12:53.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,留下实现我梦想的魔女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.85,0:12:57.89,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我跟提欧大人签订了契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是理所当然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.44,0:13:03.94,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,内曼大人已战死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.28,0:13:05.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾雪拉也身负重伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.65,0:13:08.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再增加牺牲者了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.15,0:13:10.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就以今天的战果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.78,0:13:14.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在今天向瓦尔德林申请停战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.08,0:13:21.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,停战条件是你方君主的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.17,0:13:23.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.50,0:13:25.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,既然塞维斯王已死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.59,0:13:29.34,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战争的责任就落到瓦尔林德骑士团头上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.72,0:13:32.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,因此骑士们已经没有退路了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.05,0:13:34.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗很精彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.10,0:13:38.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你这次又过火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.31,0:13:43.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谈判失败了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.19,0:13:45.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到条件居然是提欧大人的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.23,0:13:47.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.86,0:13:49.65,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,提欧大人正大光明的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.74,0:13:51.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还名正言顺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.07,0:13:55.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可是大家的性命和地位有保证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.78,0:13:56.24,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.33,0:13:59.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这种条件  我们怎么可能答应嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.58,0:14:02.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哪能抛弃提欧大人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.12,0:14:03.46,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要战到最后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.25,0:14:08.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,力量不足  真是万分抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.42,0:14:10.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里  自从遇见你之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.84,0:14:11.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我过得非常充实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.14,0:14:15.35,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然梦想破灭很遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.51,0:14:18.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过朝梦想进发的满足感更大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.98,0:14:20.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.32,0:14:32.95,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,君主提欧做好了仅留下爵位再次流浪的觉悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.57,0:14:37.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的停战条件我们应该是无法接受的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.16,0:14:39.45,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现在停战的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.62,0:14:43.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好会出现瓦尔林德骑士团败北的流言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.17,0:14:45.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来我们的武力威慑就没了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.58,0:14:47.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只要全军把城包围起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.29,0:14:49.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬间就能攻陷半毁的城池了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.01,0:14:53.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样便无法保护马丽娜大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.01,0:14:57.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔图克的佣兵神出鬼没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.43,0:15:00.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好已经潜伏在这片战场附近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.98,0:15:03.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔图克伯爵不会行动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.14,0:15:06.19,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,他都把名叫西露卡的魔法师赶走了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.27,0:15:07.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.61,0:15:10.44,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都认为阿尔图克不会行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.65,0:15:14.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,大家不觉得这样的情况非常适合行动吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.57,0:15:18.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那么  这里只留一百人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.16,0:15:19.62,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的全军一起进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.99,0:15:22.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不行只有一百人实在不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.33,0:15:24.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,马丽娜大人  请下令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.50,0:15:29.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我只问一点可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.92,0:15:32.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你们为何而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.63,0:15:35.30,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是为了克莱榭家的纹章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.18,0:15:37.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.72,0:15:40.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你们刚才说撤退会降低武力威慑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.85,0:15:42.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我是觉得  原因如果是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.85,0:15:46.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就不关克莱榭家纹章的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.23,0:15:52.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我就让你们如愿去战斗好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.15,0:15:53.69,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.28,0:15:57.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,定让敌人接受克莱榭家的制裁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.54,0:16:07.12,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,留在大本营的兵力有点少啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.71,0:16:11.13,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕他们坚信阿尔图克伯爵不会增援吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.17,0:16:14.59,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,伯爵真的不会来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.67,0:16:17.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  跟我说得很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.47,0:16:20.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,伯爵说现在不想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.89,0:16:22.85,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.56,0:16:26.98,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,假如阿尔图克伯爵等的就是这一刻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.74,0:16:42.79,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…阿尔图克伯爵的军队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.04,0:16:43.74,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.95,0:16:45.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说不会增援吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.54,0:16:54.55,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了马丽娜・克莱榭在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.22,0:16:59.09,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,维拉尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.35,0:17:04.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哟表妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.27,0:17:09.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,回大本营救援马丽娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.06,0:17:11.81,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.18,0:17:45.39,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,艾雪拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.64,0:17:47.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.77,0:17:50.02,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是醒不过来我真不知该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.31,0:17:52.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我都以为自己要挂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.27,0:17:54.61,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了普莉希拉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.32,0:18:01.20,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然能治好那么重的伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.36,0:18:03.82,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然是法尔内塞的圣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.16,0:18:07.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,都是神的旨意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.50,0:18:10.21,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.54,0:18:16.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,报告瓦尔林德骑士团伤亡惨重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.80,0:18:19.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,也许是认为无法继续战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.72,0:18:21.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,全军已经撤退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.01,0:18:23.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,总算得救了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.18,0:18:28.64,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过阿尔图克伯爵绝不是我们的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.81,0:18:30.73,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不知他会怎么处置提欧大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.31,0:18:33.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,关于阿尔图克伯爵…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.31,0:18:34.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.24,0:18:45.99,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是提欧阁下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.28,0:18:48.58,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我看过你们的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.95,0:18:50.91,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我由衷地向您致敬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.21,0:18:56.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,将我从绝境中救出来真的万分感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.75,0:18:59.63,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没事这可不单是为了你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.01,0:19:01.92,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然放跑了马丽娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过单看战果已经足够了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.26,0:19:08.18,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,好了我想商量下今后的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.26,0:19:12.43,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,伯爵首先我要为诸多冒犯向您赔罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.73,0:19:17.90,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？我不明白你为何要赔罪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.98,0:19:23.40,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？你不是跟我签订契约而美完成了使命吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.82,0:19:25.66,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让塞维斯陷入混乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,叛离了同盟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.82,0:19:31.50,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你就无需遭到魔法师协会处罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.87,0:19:34.83,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能接纳一名优秀的魔法师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.50,0:19:37.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说十全十美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.67,0:19:39.84,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.34,0:19:42.38,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那提欧大人的处置呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.55,0:19:46.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,啊我得让提欧阁下当塞维斯的盟主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.89,0:19:48.76,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我无意要求你归顺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.47,0:19:52.72,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们以联合盟友的身份并肩作战吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.60,0:20:00.48,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,塞维斯王提欧•科尔内罗子爵万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.40,0:20:03.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.86,0:20:06.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法答应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.87,0:20:12.33,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,还有别的条件吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.58,0:20:16.54,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我身为一名骑士想归属于你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.08,0:20:20.17,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,爵位只够雇西露卡一个人也无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.50,0:20:22.71,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.46,0:20:26.01,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,就是不打算交出西露卡的意思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.38,0:20:29.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这样就会践踏伯爵大人的好意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.30,0:20:32.31,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,于是就提出归顺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.97,0:20:35.52,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,男的就不想要了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.81,0:20:40.23,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在下认为归顺伯爵大人的君主里面没这类人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.56,0:20:44.07,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想必他跟西露卡•梅蕾蒂斯都能派上用场吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.40,0:20:47.11,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛既然你都这么说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.49,0:20:50.41,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过我不会封给提欧阁下领地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.53,0:20:52.03,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你得住在我的城里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.24,0:20:56.04,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,然后西露卡得待在我的魔法师团里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.25,0:20:56.87,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.41,0:20:59.42,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,在下明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.71,0:21:06.51,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…提欧大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.72,0:21:08.05,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都别说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.38,0:21:10.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我决定的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.72,0:21:13.14,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我回归骑士身离开此地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.89,0:21:16.22,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,爵位全部让给拉席克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.60,0:21:17.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.77,0:21:18.60,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.19,0:21:21.27,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过我可不打算放弃梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.86,0:21:23.86,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,终有一日我一定会回到故乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.44,0:21:25.57,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.94,0:21:29.15,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我依然要为你效忠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.78,0:21:32.49,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我的时候我哪怕抛弃一切也会赶去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.99,0:21:33.78,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.49,0:21:38.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也向神明发过誓要引导你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.00,0:21:41.08,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会跟你去阿尔图克的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.38,0:21:43.25,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,今后还请多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.84,0:21:47.26,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,想传教的话最好征得伯爵的许可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.51,0:21:50.93,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我已经没有领地就只是一名骑士而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.18,0:21:55.68,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,不就领地吗很快就又能搞到手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.76,0:21:57.06,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿如此吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.64,0:21:59.77,zhengzhong,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.12,0:17:12.29,shangzhong,,0,0,0,,提欧大人
